31 double Get(std::string const & nm) {

34  if (rObj->IsUndefined()) {
35  ThrowTypeError(std::string("Get method in psat.h: " + nm + " not present in object").c_str());

168  Get("motor_rated_voltage"), Get("motor_rated_fla"));

171  Get("motor_field_current"), Get("motor_field_voltage"));

284 NAN_METHOD(motorPerformance) {
285  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
286  r = Nan::New<Object>();
287  Motor::LineFrequency l = line();
288  double motor_rated_speed = Get("motor_rated_speed");
289  Motor::EfficiencyClass efficiencyClass = effCls();
290  double efficiency = Get("efficiency");
291  double motor_rated_power = Get("motor_rated_power");
292  double load_factor = Get("load_factor");
293  try {
294  MotorEfficiency mef(l, motor_rated_speed, efficiencyClass, motor_rated_power);
295  double mefVal = mef.calculate(load_factor, efficiency);
296  SetR("efficiency", mefVal * 100);
297  double motor_rated_voltage = Get("motor_rated_voltage");
298  double fla = Get("motor_rated_fla");
299  MotorCurrent mc(motor_rated_power, motor_rated_speed, l, efficiencyClass, efficiency, load_factor,
300  motor_rated_voltage);
301  double mcVal = mc.calculateCurrent(fla);
302  SetR("motor_current", mcVal / fla * 100);
303 
304  MotorPowerFactor motorPowerFactor(motor_rated_power, load_factor, mcVal, mefVal, motor_rated_voltage);
305  SetR("motor_power_factor", motorPowerFactor.calculate() * 100);
306  } catch (std::runtime_error const & e) {
307  std::string const what = e.what();
308  ThrowError(std::string("std::runtime_error thrown in motorPerformance - psat.h: " + what).c_str());
309  info.GetReturnValue().Set(0);
310  }
311 
312  info.GetReturnValue().Set(r);
313 }

315 NAN_METHOD(pumpEfficiency) {
316  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
317  r = Nan::New<Object>();
318  Pump::Style s = style();
319  double flow = Get("flow_rate");
320  OptimalPrePumpEff pef(s, flow);
321  double v = pef.calculate();
322  SetR("average",v);
323  double odf = OptimalDeviationFactor(flow).calculate();
324  SetR("max",v*odf);
325  info.GetReturnValue().Set(r);
